cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset or code, please cite both the paper (once available) and this repository."
title: "ISO 15189 LLM Config Experiment: Dataset and Analysis Code"
abstract: >-
  Dataset, analysis code, manuscript variants, and reproducibility materials
  for a study on LLM-assisted ISO 15189:2022 medical laboratory quality
  management system (QMS) document generation. Includes 486 generated QMS
  documents (Claude Opus 4.6 and GPT-5.4) across 9 prompt configurations and
  15 task types, 864 LLM-judge evaluations (Claude + GPT), and 30 expert
  blind-review ratings (3 raters x 10 stratified-sampled documents).
type: software
